2.2 Acres | 4 Bed | 6 Bath | 7 Car Garage + Lift

A Bold & Innovative Newly Built Estate, 15 Provence Court Is An Ultra-Luxe, Architectural Masterpiece Offering Inimitable Style, Scale, & Exquisite Design On Over 2 Acres. The Estate Boasts 4 Bedrooms, 6 Bathrooms, Including Dual Garages That Can House Up To 8 Cars. Surrounded By Magnificent Views, & Inspiring Quality, Residents Will Be Immersed In An Environment Of Creativity And Luxury. Welcome To A Truly Bespoke Lifestyle - A Once In A Lifetime Offering!

Visit 15PROVENCE.COM for more details.

Ramin Khaze @khaze.re

node.text:
📍190 Curtis Road, Woodmere NY $7,000,000
__
Welcome to a state of the art new construction in the highly sought after Hewlett Neck. This magnificent 8000 sqft cul de sac home is located closer to the water than any of its neighbors and boasts gorgeous relaxing views of the marina and nature.

The home is equipped with the newest technology to accommodate luxury living in comfort with touch panel controls in different areas of the house for every feature. There is radiant heat under the flooring, and elegant glow from the halo lighting in the ceilings all across the house.

Amazing double height ceilings open the spacious living room and foyer for a grand feeling with spaces for chandeliers. Each bedroom features an attached bathroom. The grand master suite does not fall shy of what you would expect from a house like this. Wide space, with his and hers walk-in closets accompanied by a spacious master bathroom with space for a tub and walk-in shower is everyone’s dream, simply magnificent.

The outdoor area comes equipped with surround sound systems and offers a luxurious cabana with an outdoor kitchen, a new dock and bulkhead with a resort-like pool and jacuzzi to complete this marvelous house. Finding a state of the art new construction with this proximity to the water and smart home features to accommodate maximum comfort and luxury will just not happen again. View this house now and make it your own with finishes of your choice to fit this home to your style today!
__
#NestSeekers #HewlettNeck #Woodmere
Listing: @Andy_Kim_1015, @NevoYemini

Visit NestSeekers.com, WebID: 1907523
